{"tid":2405048,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"IG 新策阻 TikTok 影片轉載 有水印者直接減曝光率","createTime":"2021-02-12T05:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T14:34:24.000Z","uid":48083,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"efc788a8e87084c4c7855d72145ece97f2f680e0","tid":2405048,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T05:50:00.000Z","msg":"早前 Instagram 在限時動態的欄位推出Reels功能，性質像 TikTok 一樣，讓用家可以編輯和錄製 15 秒的短片，再配以不同音樂和特效上傳到 Instagram，現時只開放在美國市場及其他50個國家。最近 Instagram 宣佈，為防止TikTok影片在Instagram 不停出現，將修改演算法，亦提供了使用貼士，告訴 Reels 用家如何令影片提高曝光率和宣傳度。<br />\n<br />\nInstagram建議 Reels 用家使用 Instagram 音樂庫，錄製直向的影片，亦提議帶領潮流，例如風靡一時的跳舞影片，或其他有趣的影片，讓其他用家可以參與。影片有大量文字、模糊不清、有水印或 Logo、有邊框的便不會被經常推薦給其他用家⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/02/12/instagram-newfeaturereels/life-tech/social-network/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F02%2F12%2Finstagram-newfeaturereels%2Flife-tech%2Fsocial-network%2F&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FG%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=6fd46ce7\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/02/12/instagram-newfeaturereels/life-tech/social-network/</a>"},{"pid":"fd1ab99f7b4becff4cd6e3d6e280a54662469d57","tid":2405048,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T05:50:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87e2e9f4ea2e03f6494929642b65985381c6635b","tid":2405048,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T05:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73390cbb101c6b10ed9ca0d6ea9bf1ef9f5d0ff9","tid":2405048,"uid":3177,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T05:52:34.000Z","msg":"抖佢老母臭<br />\n不過兩個都大仆街 打和"},{"pid":"d6d4eb16d656d39b393ad0ab239e6ae7278224a7","tid":2405048,"uid":3852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:16:39.000Z","msg":"直頭ban 9 埋佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab911ea0d34c569f